{{Infobox journal | title = Acta Koreana | discipline = [[Korean studies]] | abbreviation = Acta Koreana | editor = Tschung-Sun Kim | publisher = Academia Koreana, [[Keimyung University]] | country = Korea | frequency = Biannually | history = 1998-present | website = http://actakoreana.org | | | ISSN = 1520-7412 | OCLC = 834987973 | LCCN = 99110939 }} '''''Acta Koreana''''' is a biannual [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering [[Korean studies]] published in English by Academia Koreana ([[Keimyung University]]). It was established in 1998 as an annual publication; since 2002 it has been published biannually.
== Abstracting and indexing == The journal is abstracted and indexed in the [[Arts & Humanities Citation Index]], [[Current Contents]]/Arts & Humanities,<ref name=ISI>{{cite web |url=http://ip-science.thomsonreuters.com/mjl/ |title=Master Journal List |publisher=[[Thomson Reuters]] |work=Intellectual Property & Science |accessdate=2018-09-25}}</ref> [[Scopus]],<ref name=Scopus>{{cite web|url=http://cdn.elsevier.com/assets/excel_doc/0003/148548/title_list.xlsx |title=Scopus title list |format=[[Microsoft Excel]] |publisher=[[Elsevier]] |work= |accessdate=2018-09-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202041814/http://cdn.elsevier.com/assets/excel_doc/0003/148548/title_list.xlsx |archivedate=2013-12-02 }}</ref> [[CSA Sociological Abstracts]], [[Bibliography of Asian Studies]],[[Korea Citation Index]], and [[SocINDEX]].
